# Threat Hunting Rules

## Method
Follow [[Hunt Methodology]]. Convert outcomes into detections or IR improvements.

## IDs & Registry
- Assign `ES-HUNT-####`
- Register in [[Hunts Index]]

## Note Structure
Hypothesis → Scope → Data → Method → Findings → Outcomes → Related Notes

## Quality
- Distinguish evidence from interpretation.
- Record negative results; they have value.
